        scene_name = ["Lyon, France", "New Tokyo, Japan", "Chang an, China", "New York", "Berlin", "Starport One"]
        scene_descrip = ["As night embraced the city, the glow from a modest room whispered tales of warmth. Here, amidst the embrace of wood and paper, the world outside seemed a distant memory, leaving only the gentle flow of time. Pages fluttered like the melody of the night, vividly narrating tales of distant lands. Amidst this tranquility, the room became a vessel, sailing across the vast ocean of stars, laden with dreams and longing.", "Where light and shadow interlace, the breath of the future permeates every corner. The room, a nexus of dreams and reality, hums with the promise of tomorrow with every surge of data. Here, technology is not cold but alive with the warmth and pulse of humanity. Beneath the night sky, every nook of Neo-Tokyo thrums with poetic explorations of the unknown—a limitless ode to the future, awaiting its chronicle, its discovery.", "Under the tender gaze of the moon, a sanctuary of wisdom nestled quietly. The scent of ink mingled with the essence of ancient paper, weaving a silent symphony in the serene night. Shadows danced softly beneath the solitary lamp, each stroke and character a whisper from the past. Here, the night was not merely darkness but a journey, meandering through verses of a thousand years, in search of a soulmate never met.", "In 1960s New York, the city buzzed with a vibrant mix of history and modernity. Inside a cozy room, the air was thick with the era's essence: vinyl records on the walls, an old typewriter on a wooden desk, and soft jazz drifting in from an open window. This cultural melting pot attracted diverse individuals, each carving out their space and voice.Amid this dynamic setting, the room served as a hub of creativity, mirroring the exciting societal shifts of the time. The rhythms of New York, the street bustle, neon-lit nights, and cultural gatherings painted a vivid picture of life, capturing the spirit of the decade.", "In 19th century Berlin, the air buzzed with intellectual fervor and artistic flourish. Nestled within a modest yet elegant study, walls lined with towering bookcases and adorned with fine art, the spirit of the Enlightenment thrived. A grand piano stood by a large window, through which the soft glow of gaslights filtered, casting gentle shadows. Here, amidst the rustle of scholarly papers and the rich aroma of leather-bound books, the room resonated with the echoes of philosophical debates and the melodies of classical compositions, capturing the essence of an era dedicated to cultural and intellectual refinement.", "When the darkness of the universe envelops everything, the lights in the space station flicker faintly, with the metallic walls reflecting a dim blue glow, as if whispering. Outside the window, the stars flow quietly, distant and indifferent, yet inside, there is a sense of solitary tranquility. The sound of keyboard clicks occasionally breaks the silence, like an echo from the depths of space. At this moment, the space station seems to be the only existence in the universe, carrying endless exploration and a longing for the unknown, drifting in the sea of stars, watching over the boundless future."]
